==English==

===Noun===
'''cupboard'''  (''plural:'' '''[[cupboards]]''') Pronounced "ku-verd" It sounds identical to the word "covered". It is commonly mispronounced "ku-berd" or "kup-bord"
# An enclosed, non "walk-in" storage space with a door as a means of access. Usually to be found in a kitchen
#:"Put the cups in the cupboard"
# {{colloquial}}: A small room.

